snippet.title: Pirate Radio Trailer - Global Game Jam 2018
snippet.description:
On the high seas, broadcast your illegal radio tunes to the masses, while avoiding the marine police. Switch between managing your radio playlist and steering your vessel in an effort to keep your listeners happy.
Pirate Radio is a game made in 48 hours by Jonathan Hopkins and Alex Grace during the Global Game Jam 2018. Music was provided by mbryo.
Play the game at: https://globalgamejam.org/2018/games/pirate-radio-0
